<subSubSection id="B77C935318C726C3C3C3B03B5378342E" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="3DFBD15731CEF19F476382756B43ED87" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FFA50B28ABF6701B00433633C9C63388" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Cachoeira is Portuguese for cascade or waterfall, in reference to the habitat where the species was collected.</paragraph>
